                    android:layout_margin="@dimen/cardMarginVertical"
                    android:textColor="@color/md_grey_900"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="A. Accommodation will be provided from 23rd February, 4 p.m. for four days.
B. Participants are required to report at Registration Desk as soon as they arrive at the campus.
C. All students must carry valid College photo ID card and bring 2 passport sized photos.
D. Facilities provided:
    1: Passes to all exhibitions.
    2: Passes to all think talks.
    3: Passes to Kaleidoscope.
    4: Hospitality kit
E. Technex will not be responsible for the security of belongings of participants.
F. Participants are to bring the materials for their respective events.
G. The decision of Technex team will be final in all disputes.

Contacts:
Rohit Negi- +919459494009
Rahul Yadav- +919956443498"/>


